<data>&lt;div class=b&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1"&gt;12S1 Sagāthāvaggasaṃyuttapāḷi&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1/7"&gt;7 Brāhmaṇasaṃyutta&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1/7/7.1"&gt;7.1 Arahantavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="i"&gt;7.1.3 Asurindakasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Brāhmaṇasaṃyutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Arahantavagga&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Asurindakasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_1150"&gt; &lt;div class="divNumber"&gt;189.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;1150&lt;/span&gt;Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. Assosi kho asurindakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo—  “bhāradvājagotto brāhmaṇo kira samaṇassa gotamassa santike agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito”ti kupito anattamano yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ asabbhāhi pharusāhi vācāhi akkosati paribhāsati. Evaṃ vutte, bhagavā tuṇhī ahosi. Atha kho asurindakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca—  “jitosi, samaṇa, jitosi, samaṇā”ti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_1151"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;1151&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Jayaṃ ve maññati bālo,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;vācāya pharusaṃ bhaṇaṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Jayañcevassa taṃ hoti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;yā titikkhā vijānato.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_1152"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;1152&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Tasseva tena pāpiyo,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;yo kuddhaṃ paṭikujjhati;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Kuddhaṃ appaṭikujjhanto,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;saṅgāmaṃ jeti dujjayaṃ.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_1153"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;1153&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Ubhinnamatthaṃ carati,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;attano ca parassa ca;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Paraṃ saṅkupitaṃ ñatvā,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;yo sato upasammati.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_1154"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;1154&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Ubhinnaṃ tikicchantānaṃ,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;attano ca parassa ca;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Janā maññanti bāloti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;ye dhammassa akovidā”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_1155"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;1155&lt;/span&gt;Evaṃ vutte, asurindakabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca—  “abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama…pe…  abbhaññāsi. Aññataro ca panāyasmā bhāradvājo arahataṃ ahosīti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="tn"&gt;&lt;div class=plcb&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="prevP()" id="prevL" name="273802" title="Go to previous page"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; 7.1.2 Akkosasutta&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="upP()" id="upL" name="272707" title="Go to parent page"&gt;up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="nextP()" id="nextL" name="273804" title="Go to next page"&gt;7.1.4 Bilaṅgikasutta &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</data>
